<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Schemavalidationexception on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/schemavalidationexception/</link><description>Recent content in Schemavalidationexception on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/schemavalidationexception/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Java SchemaValidationException — XML Schema Validation Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/schemavalidationexception/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/schemavalidationexception/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="schemavalidationexception--xml-schema-validation-fix"&gt;SchemaValidationException — XML Schema Validation Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;SchemaValidationException&lt;/code&gt; (or &lt;code&gt;SAXException&lt;/code&gt; subclass from schema validation) is thrown when an XML document fails validation against its XSD (XML Schema Definition). This typically occurs when using JAXP, JAXB, or SAX-based XML processing with schema validation enabled.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Schema validation checks that an XML document conforms to the structure, data types, and constraints defined in its associated XSD schema. Common error messages include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;cvc-complex-type.2.4.a: Invalid content was found starting with element 'elementName'&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;cvc-type.3.1.3: The value 'value' of element 'elementName' is not valid&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;cvc-attribute.1.2: Element 'elementName' has no attribute 'attrName'&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;cvc-enumeration.1: The value 'value' is not valid for restriction&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: XML element not defined in the schema&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;String xml &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;lt;root&amp;gt;&amp;lt;unknownElement&amp;gt;data&amp;lt;/unknownElement&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/root&amp;gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Schema defines: &amp;lt;root&amp;gt;&amp;lt;knownElement/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/root&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Wrong data type for an element&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;String xml &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;lt;user&amp;gt;&amp;lt;age&amp;gt;not-a-number&amp;lt;/age&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/user&amp;gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Schema defines: &amp;lt;xs:element name=&amp;#34;age&amp;#34; type=&amp;#34;xs:integer&amp;#34;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Missing required element or attribute&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;String xml &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;lt;order&amp;gt;&amp;lt;item&amp;gt;book&amp;lt;/item&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/order&amp;gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Schema requires: &amp;lt;order&amp;gt;&amp;lt;id/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;item/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/order&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Namespace mismatch&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;String xml &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&amp;lt;ns:root xmlns:ns=\&amp;#34;http://wrong.namespace.com\&amp;#34;/&amp;gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Schema namespace: http://correct.namespace.com&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="solutions"&gt;Solutions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-enable-and-configure-jaxp-schema-validation-properly"&gt;Fix 1: Enable and configure JAXP schema validation properly&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; javax.xml.XMLConstants;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; javax.xml.parsers.SAXParserFactory;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;SAXParserFactory factory &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; SAXParserFactory.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;newInstance&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;factory.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setNamespaceAware&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;factory.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setValidating&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Enable schema validation&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;factory.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setProperty&lt;/span&gt;(XMLConstants.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;W&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;XMLSchema槊_NS_URI,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;factory.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setProperty&lt;/span&gt;(XMLConstants.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;JAXP_SCHEMA_LANGUAGE&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;factory.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setProperty&lt;/span&gt;(XMLConstants.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;JAXP_SCHEMA_SOURCE&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; File(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;schema.xsd&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;SAXParser parser &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; factory.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;newSAXParser&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;parser.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parse&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; File(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;document.xml&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;), &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; DefaultHandler());
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-validate-xml-against-schema-before-processing"&gt;Fix 2: Validate XML against schema before processing&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; javax.xml.transform.stream.StreamSource;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; javax.xml.validation.Schema;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; javax.xml.validation.SchemaFactory;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; javax.xml.validation.Validator;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; java.io.File;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;SchemaFactory schemaFactory &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; SchemaFactory.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;newInstance&lt;/span&gt;(XMLConstants.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;W3C_XML_SCHEMA_NS_URI&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Schema schema &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; schemaFactory.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;newSchema&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; File(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;schema.xsd&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Validator validator &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; schema.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;newValidator&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; validator.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;validate&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; StreamSource(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; File(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;document.xml&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; System.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;XML is valid&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (SAXException e) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; System.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;XML validation failed: &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; e.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getMessage&lt;/span&gt;());
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-fix-the-xml-document-to-match-the-schema"&gt;Fix 3: Fix the XML document to match the schema&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;!-- Wrong — missing required element and wrong type --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;user&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;name&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;Alice&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/name&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;age&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;not-a-number&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/age&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/user&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;!-- Correct — matches schema definition --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;user&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;xmlns=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;http://example.com/schema&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;name&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;Alice&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/name&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;age&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;30&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/age&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;/user&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-use-custom-error-handler-for-detailed-validation-messages"&gt;Fix 4: Use custom error handler for detailed validation messages&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; org.xml.sax.SAXException;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; org.xml.sax.SAXParseException;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Schema schema &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; schemaFactory.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;newSchema&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; File(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;schema.xsd&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Validator validator &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; schema.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;newValidator&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;validator.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setErrorHandler&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; ErrorHandler() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Override&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;warning&lt;/span&gt;(SAXParseException e) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; System.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Warning: &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; e.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getMessage&lt;/span&gt;());
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Override&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;error&lt;/span&gt;(SAXParseException e) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; System.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Error at line &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; e.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getLineNumber&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; e.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getMessage&lt;/span&gt;());
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Override&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fatalError&lt;/span&gt;(SAXParseException e) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; System.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Fatal: &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; e.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getMessage&lt;/span&gt;());
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="prevention-checklist"&gt;Prevention Checklist&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Always validate XML against its schema before processing critical data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use a custom &lt;code&gt;ErrorHandler&lt;/code&gt; to capture all validation errors, not just the first.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure namespace URIs in XML documents match those in the XSD schema.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Test schema validation with both valid and invalid XML documents.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="../saxparseexception"&gt;SAXParseException&lt;/a&gt; — detailed parsing error with line/column info.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="../xmlstreamexception"&gt;XMLStreamException&lt;/a&gt; — StAX-based XML processing error.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="../ioexception"&gt;IOException&lt;/a&gt; — file not found or read error for schema/XML files.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>